Gaupol 0.20
===========

 [/] Migrate to Python 3, GTK+ 3, GNOME 3 and PyGI
     * Test encoding auto-detection
     * Check API documentation on aeidon.as_* and aeidon.is_*
     * Check if GtkSpell is availabel with PyGI support
     * Fix remaining regressions (search for 'XXX:')
     * Check video toolbar spacing etc.
 [/] Bump Python dependency to 3.2 or greater
 [/] Replace PyGTK dependency with PyGobject 3.0.0 or greater
 [/] Rewrite line-breaking algorithm to use a Knuth-Plass-style flexible
     system of penalties and a versatile measure of goodness
 [X] Add 48x48 and 256x256 pixel PNG icons and remove SVG icon
 [X] Update Brazilian Portuguese translation
     (Átila Camurça, Darlildo Lima)

Gaupol 1.0
==========

 * Add a built-in GStreamer-based video player
 * Add a GStreamer-based audio waveform display

